+ Eclipse build S-3.2M4-200512151506

Target environment:
+ Eclipse build S-3.2M4-200512151506

+ GEF Build I20051213

java.lang.UnsupportedClassVersionError:
org/eclipse/gmf/examples/taipan/gmf/editor/part/TaiPanDiagramEditorPlugin

Perhaps, launch configuration uses incorrect JRE (not Java 5)?
Wrong JRE version was indeed the problem.
The cause for the problem is wrong launch configuration. Resolved.
